1
00:00:07,440 --> 00:00:09,576
Narrator: CAESAR WAS
THE SON OF MARIO ZEPPELI,

2
00:00:09,643 --> 00:00:12,012
CONSIDERED THE BEST FURNITURE
MAKER IN ALL OF NAPLES.

3
00:00:12,078 --> 00:00:15,415
MARIO WAS A PROPER
ITALIAN MAN OF HIS DAY,

4
00:00:15,481 --> 00:00:17,518
THOROUGHLY DEDICATED
TO HIS FAMILY.

5
00:00:17,584 --> 00:00:20,787
TO CAESAR,
HE WAS THE IDEAL MAN.

6
00:00:21,655 --> 00:00:23,356
WHEN CAESAR WAS 10,

7
00:00:23,456 --> 00:00:26,660
MARIO SUDDENLY LEFT
WITHOUT SO MUCH AS A WORD.

8
00:00:26,693 --> 00:00:29,663
HAVING LOST THEIR MOTHER
YEARS BEFORE, THEY WERE ALONE.

9
00:00:29,696 --> 00:00:32,465
DISTANT RELATIVES
STOLE WHAT LITTLE THEY HAD.

10
00:00:32,533 --> 00:00:34,868
CAESAR BECAME A DELINQUENT,

11
00:00:34,935 --> 00:00:39,540
GROWING TO HATE HIS FATHER
AND WHAT HE HAD DONE TO THEM.

12
00:00:39,606 --> 00:00:41,708
( Caesar groans )
I BET HE'S LIVING CAREFREE

13
00:00:41,775 --> 00:00:43,376
WITH SOME HOT YOUNG WOMAN!

14
00:00:43,443 --> 00:00:45,879
I'LL GONNA FIND HIM
AND THEN KILL HIM!

15
00:00:45,979 --> 00:00:49,382
Narrator: HE THREW AWAY
HIS YOUTH AND HIS FUTURE.

16
00:00:49,449 --> 00:00:52,485
HE COMMITTED THEFT,
ARSON, ASSAULT,

17
00:00:52,553 --> 00:00:55,221
ANYTHING SHORT
OF OUTRIGHT MURDER.

18
00:00:55,321 --> 00:00:57,791
EVEN THE LOCAL MAFIOSOS
FEARED HIM.

19
00:00:57,858 --> 00:01:00,493
Man: HEY, YOU'RE THAT GUY
NAMED CAESAR, AREN'T YOU?

20
00:01:00,561 --> 00:01:02,068
SO WHAT'S YOUR LAST NAME?

21
00:01:02,135 --> 00:01:03,537
Caesar: I DON'T HAVE ONE.

22
00:01:03,570 --> 00:01:05,405
( man laughs )
WELL, THAT MEANS

23
00:01:05,471 --> 00:01:07,007
THERE'S NO WAY YOU'RE ITALIANO.

24
00:01:07,073 --> 00:01:10,143
ITALIANOS ARE PROUD
OF THEIR FAMILY NAMES.

25
00:01:10,210 --> 00:01:11,578
Narrator: NEVER HOLDING BACK,

26
00:01:11,645 --> 00:01:14,581
HE OFTEN STARTED STARTED FIGHTS
BY USING A WRENCH

27
00:01:14,648 --> 00:01:16,583
TO SUDDENLY BASH
HIS OPPONENT'S HEAD

28
00:01:16,650 --> 00:01:18,752
BEFORE CALMLY
FINISHING THEM OFF.

29
00:01:20,587 --> 00:01:22,723
THOUGH HE DIDN'T KNOW IT YET,

30
00:01:22,756 --> 00:01:26,059
HE WAS ALREADY
BEGINNING TO USE HAMON.

31
00:01:26,092 --> 00:01:28,895
THEN, AT AGE 16 IN ROME...

32
00:01:28,929 --> 00:01:29,896
( Caesar gasping )

33
00:01:29,930 --> 00:01:31,865
♪

34
00:01:31,932 --> 00:01:35,101
THERE'S NO MISTAKE.
IT'S REALLY HIM.

35
00:01:35,168 --> 00:01:36,837
Narrator: AT THAT MOMENT,

36
00:01:36,903 --> 00:01:39,773
CAESAR FELT HE MIGHT MURDER
HIS OWN FATHER.

37
00:01:40,941 --> 00:01:41,842
BUT THEN...

38
00:01:41,908 --> 00:01:46,012
( Caesar gasps )
W‐WHAT IS ALL THAT?

39
00:01:46,079 --> 00:01:47,113
HUH?

40
00:01:48,348 --> 00:01:51,451
THAT'S A MASSIVE DIAMOND.

41
00:01:51,552 --> 00:01:55,121
Mario: NO!
BOY, DON'T TOUCH THAT STONE!

42
00:01:55,188 --> 00:01:56,890
Caesar: IT'S YOU!

43
00:01:56,957 --> 00:01:57,958
( gasps )

44
00:01:58,058 --> 00:02:01,101
W‐WHAT THE HELL
IS THE WALL DOING?

45
00:02:01,134 --> 00:02:02,268
( Mario screams )

46
00:02:02,302 --> 00:02:04,538
( Caesar grunts )

47
00:02:04,605 --> 00:02:06,640
Mario: STAY BACK.

48
00:02:06,707 --> 00:02:08,141
THIS IS ALL A TRAP.

49
00:02:08,241 --> 00:02:09,409
( gags )

50
00:02:09,475 --> 00:02:11,578
Narrator: EVENTS HAD
OCCURRED 50 YEARS AGO

51
00:02:11,645 --> 00:02:13,479
THAT WERE COMPLETELY UNKNOWN
TO CAESAR.

52
00:02:13,580 --> 00:02:16,216
HIS GRANDFATHER WILL
HAD DIED TRAGICALLY

53
00:02:16,282 --> 00:02:17,617
WHILE ON AN EXPEDITION.

54
00:02:17,651 --> 00:02:19,619
MARIO TOOK UP HIS FATHER'S TORCH

55
00:02:19,653 --> 00:02:21,822
AND TRAINED WITH HAMON
TO PREPARE,

56
00:02:21,922 --> 00:02:24,424
DISCOVERING THE RUINS
SOON AFTER.

57
00:02:24,490 --> 00:02:25,959
HE BEGAN A WORLDWIDE SEARCH

58
00:02:25,992 --> 00:02:28,595
FOR A WAY TO DEFEAT
THE MONSTERS WITHIN

59
00:02:28,662 --> 00:02:30,764
AND UNLOCK
THE TREASURE THEY HIDE,

60
00:02:30,831 --> 00:02:32,833
BUT CAESAR KNEW NONE OF THIS.

61
00:02:32,899 --> 00:02:36,436
Mario: YOUNG MAN,
I BEG FROM YOU A FAVOR.

62
00:02:36,503 --> 00:02:37,738
MAKE YOUR WAY TO VENICE,

63
00:02:37,804 --> 00:02:39,906
AND SPEAK WITH A WOMAN
NAMED LISA LISA.

64
00:02:39,973 --> 00:02:41,808
IT'S A MATTER OF LIFE AND DEATH.

65
00:02:41,842 --> 00:02:45,011
SHE IS THE ONLY ONE WHO HAS
ANY CHANCE OF STOPPING THEM.

66
00:02:45,111 --> 00:02:47,948
Narrator: PERHAPS BECAUSE
SO MANY YEARS HAD PASSED

67
00:02:48,014 --> 00:02:51,451
AND CAESAR HAD GROWN,
MARIO DID NOT RECOGNIZE HIS SON.

68
00:02:51,518 --> 00:02:53,019
Caesar: FA...

69
00:02:53,086 --> 00:02:55,188
Narrator: CAESAR'S FATHER
HADN'T ABANDONED HIS FAMILY

70
00:02:55,288 --> 00:02:56,990
‐ FOR SELFISH REASONS.
‐ Mario: HURRY! PLEASE FIND HER!

71
00:02:57,023 --> 00:02:59,660
Narrator: HE'D LEFT IN ORDER
TO KEEP HIS CHILDREN SAFE

72
00:02:59,693 --> 00:03:01,467
FROM THE NIGHTMARE
OF THE PILLAR MEN.

73
00:03:01,535 --> 00:03:05,038
‐ ( blood draining )
‐ ( heart beating )

74
00:03:05,105 --> 00:03:08,208
♪

75
00:03:08,308 --> 00:03:11,377
( Caesar gasps ) FATHER!

76
00:03:11,444 --> 00:03:13,547
( cries )

77
00:03:22,556 --> 00:03:24,725
♪

78
00:03:29,195 --> 00:03:31,131
( singing in Japanese )

79
00:04:55,556 --> 00:04:57,958
♪

80
00:04:57,991 --> 00:04:59,826
JoJo: I SEE.

81
00:04:59,926 --> 00:05:01,835
Lisa Lisa:
CAESAR'S MISUNDERSTANDING

82
00:05:01,902 --> 00:05:05,672
LED TO A DEEP HATRED,
BUT THEN THAT CHANGED.

83
00:05:05,739 --> 00:05:08,809
IT BECAME PRIDE IN HIS FATHER
AND HIS FAMILY.

84
00:05:08,842 --> 00:05:11,177
SO CAESAR SOUGHT ME OUT

85
00:05:11,244 --> 00:05:14,480
AND PICKED UP
WHERE HIS FATHER HAD LEFT OFF.

86
00:05:14,515 --> 00:05:18,685
JoJo: HE'S GOING, BECAUSE HE
NEEDS TO AVENGE HIS FATHER.

87
00:05:18,752 --> 00:05:20,854
FORGIVE ME, CAESAR.

88
00:05:20,921 --> 00:05:24,324
I DIDN'T MEAN TO SPEAK ILL
OF YOUR BRAVE FAMILY.

89
00:05:25,759 --> 00:05:28,028
IF YOU STILL WANT
TO GO CHARGING IN THERE

90
00:05:28,128 --> 00:05:31,331
EVEN THOUGH YOU KNOW DAMN WELL
IT'S GOING TO BE A TRAP,

91
00:05:31,364 --> 00:05:34,334
THEN YOU MUST HAVE FIGURED OUT
SOME WAY TO BEAT KARS.

92
00:05:34,367 --> 00:05:35,702
CHANGED MY MIND.

93
00:05:35,769 --> 00:05:38,371
SINCE YOU'RE GOING
IN THAT DERELICT HELLHOLE,

94
00:05:38,471 --> 00:05:41,875
THEN I'M RIGHT BEHIND YOU,
CAESAR ZEPPELI.

95
00:05:41,975 --> 00:05:43,176
( Caesar grunts )

96
00:05:43,209 --> 00:05:46,880
A SET OF FOOTPRINTS
LEADS INTO THE MANSION.

97
00:05:48,448 --> 00:05:49,382
( gasps )

98
00:05:49,482 --> 00:05:51,952
( wind blowing )

99
00:05:53,219 --> 00:05:54,287
♪

100
00:05:54,354 --> 00:05:55,388
( gasps ) WHO WAS THAT?

101
00:05:55,488 --> 00:05:58,324
I SWEAR I SAW SOMEONE THERE.

102
00:05:58,391 --> 00:05:59,826
AM I HALLUCINATING?

103
00:06:00,801 --> 00:06:01,735
THERE IT IS!

104
00:06:01,802 --> 00:06:02,836
IT'S NOT AN ILLUSION!

105
00:06:02,903 --> 00:06:05,972
WHAT THE HELL IS THAT?!

106
00:06:06,039 --> 00:06:07,874
( male voice )
CAESAR!

107
00:06:10,577 --> 00:06:13,479
( Caesar gasps )
HE VANISHED.

108
00:06:13,547 --> 00:06:15,849
BUT I KNOW HE'S HERE, CLOSE.

109
00:06:15,916 --> 00:06:18,051
HE'S WITHIN A FEW STEPS OF ME.

110
00:06:18,084 --> 00:06:20,420
DOES KARS HAVE
SOME KIND OF NEW TRICK?

111
00:06:20,486 --> 00:06:23,590
NO, THE SUN IS SHINING
TOO STRONG FOR HIM.

112
00:06:23,690 --> 00:06:25,859
HE CAN'T BE OUT HERE
AND SURVIVE.

113
00:06:25,926 --> 00:06:27,561
Narrator: THE CAT STANCE,

114
00:06:27,594 --> 00:06:29,763
A FUNDAMENTAL ELEMENT
OF KUNG FU.

115
00:06:29,830 --> 00:06:32,032
CAESAR HAS
NEVER HEARD OF KUNG FU,

116
00:06:32,098 --> 00:06:34,267
BUT INSTINCTIVELY
BALANCES HIS STANCE

117
00:06:34,367 --> 00:06:35,869
AS HE RELAXES HIS LIMBS,

118
00:06:35,936 --> 00:06:37,871
READY FOR ATTACK
FROM ANY DIRECTION.

119
00:06:37,938 --> 00:06:41,274
FOR HIM, IT IS NOT A TECHNIQUE,
BUT A REFLEX.

120
00:06:41,341 --> 00:06:43,276
‐ Meshina: CAESAR.
‐ ( Caesar gasps )

121
00:06:43,343 --> 00:06:45,111
Meshina: WHAT DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE DOING?

122
00:06:45,178 --> 00:06:46,947
GOING IN THERE ALL ALONE
IS MADNESS.

123
00:06:47,013 --> 00:06:48,782
Caesar: JUST STAY BACK,
INSTRUCTOR!

124
00:06:48,849 --> 00:06:52,052
I CAN'T MOVE AT ALL,
LET ALONE GO RUSHING IN.

125
00:06:52,118 --> 00:06:55,088
SOMETHING IS HIDING JUST INSIDE
THE ENTRANCE OF THE BUILDING.

126
00:06:55,121 --> 00:06:56,557
Meshina: WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

127
00:06:56,623 --> 00:06:58,625
I CAN'T SEE A THING IN THERE.

128
00:06:58,725 --> 00:06:59,793
HUH?

129
00:06:59,860 --> 00:07:01,635
A‐‐A SINGLE FOOTPRINT
JUST APPEARED.

130
00:07:01,702 --> 00:07:02,803
Caesar: HE MUST HAVE JUMPED.

131
00:07:02,903 --> 00:07:05,572
HE'S COMING AT US FROM ABOVE!
THERE!

132
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:09,543
WHAT THE‐‐

133
00:07:09,610 --> 00:07:11,778
WAMUU!

134
00:07:11,812 --> 00:07:14,047
( Wamuu growls )

135
00:07:15,481 --> 00:07:16,650
( Meshina groans )

136
00:07:16,750 --> 00:07:18,451
( screaming )

137
00:07:18,484 --> 00:07:21,054
Caesar: INSTRUCTOR, NO!

138
00:07:22,989 --> 00:07:24,490
WHAT THE HELL IS THIS?

139
00:07:24,591 --> 00:07:25,826
THAT GUY WAS WAMUU.

140
00:07:25,892 --> 00:07:28,294
ARE HE AND KARS
INSIDE THAT MANSION TOGETHER?

141
00:07:28,328 --> 00:07:32,999
BUT WAIT A MINUTE. HOW CAN WAMUU
COME OUTSIDE DURING THE DAY?

142
00:07:33,066 --> 00:07:36,169
HE DID LOOK KIND OF GHOSTLIKE.

143
00:07:42,843 --> 00:07:44,010
Wamuu: WHERE IS HE,

144
00:07:44,110 --> 00:07:46,446
THAT INFURIATING
SMART‐TALKING UPSTART?

145
00:07:46,513 --> 00:07:50,951
I HEAR TELL THAT JOJO
HAS LEARNED QUITE A BIT.

146
00:07:51,017 --> 00:07:53,754
WHERE IS THE MAN
WHO KILLED MASTER ESIDISI?

147
00:07:53,820 --> 00:07:55,656
Caesar: WIND.

148
00:07:55,689 --> 00:07:57,958
WAMUU CAN CONTROL THE WIND.

149
00:07:58,024 --> 00:08:00,026
THAT'S WHY
HE'S DIFFICULT TO SEE.

150
00:08:00,126 --> 00:08:02,803
AIR'S COMING FROM PIPES
IN HIS CHEST.

151
00:08:02,869 --> 00:08:04,705
HE'S ONLY SLIGHTLY VISIBLE

152
00:08:04,805 --> 00:08:08,842
BECAUSE OF WATER VAPOR SWIRLING
IN THE FLOW AROUND HIS BODY.

153
00:08:08,875 --> 00:08:09,976
I'VE GOT IT!

154
00:08:10,043 --> 00:08:11,878
HE'S CLOAKING HIMSELF IN VAPOR

155
00:08:11,978 --> 00:08:13,947
THAT HE'S GENERATING
FROM THE AIR,

156
00:08:14,014 --> 00:08:16,382
AND THEN HE'S PUMPING IT
OUT OF THOSE PIPES.

157
00:08:16,449 --> 00:08:20,386
IT'S REFRACTING LIGHT
LIKE A MILLION TINY PRISMS.

158
00:08:20,453 --> 00:08:23,156
IT'S A SUIT
THAT BENDS LIGHT AROUND HIM,

159
00:08:23,223 --> 00:08:25,158
PROTECTING HIM
FROM THE SUN'S RAYS,

160
00:08:25,225 --> 00:08:27,060
THUS ALLOWING HIM TO BE OUTSIDE.

161
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:30,797
THAT'S WHY
HE SEEMS TO BE TRANSPARENT.

162
00:08:30,864 --> 00:08:32,899
Wamuu: TOO BAD JOJO ISN'T HERE.

163
00:08:32,999 --> 00:08:36,870
YOU ARE THE BUBBLE USER
NAMED CAESAR, ARE YOU NOT?

164
00:08:36,903 --> 00:08:38,872
SIMPLY BY LOOKING
INTO YOUR EYES,

165
00:08:38,905 --> 00:08:40,907
I CAN SEE
THAT YOU'VE ALSO LEARNED MUCH

166
00:08:41,007 --> 00:08:43,910
THOUGH YOUR ORDEALS.

167
00:08:43,977 --> 00:08:45,712
VERY WELL!

168
00:08:45,746 --> 00:08:48,915
YOU ARE WORTHY OF DEATH
AT MY HANDS, BUBBLE USER!

169
00:08:48,982 --> 00:08:51,552
( Caesar yells )
WE'LL SEE WHO DIES!

170
00:08:52,653 --> 00:08:54,087
I FEEL LIKE I DID BACK THEN,

171
00:08:54,187 --> 00:08:55,722
WHEN I WAS NA ÏVE AND POOR,

172
00:08:55,756 --> 00:08:58,659
BACK WHEN YOU VICIOUSLY
TOOK THE LIFE OF MY FATHER.

173
00:08:58,725 --> 00:09:03,036
AND NOW I'LL USE MY VICIOUSNESS
TO DESTROY YOU!

174
00:09:05,338 --> 00:09:07,207
VERY IMPRESSIVE,
BUT DON'T THINK YOUR WIND

175
00:09:07,273 --> 00:09:09,843
WILL BE ABLE TO JUST
BLOW MY BUBBLES AWAY.

176
00:09:09,910 --> 00:09:13,346
SOME BUBBLES
GO RIGHT THROUGH WIND.

177
00:09:13,413 --> 00:09:17,618
I'VE SIGNIFICANTLY UPDATED
MY GRANDFATHER'S HAMON CUTTER.

178
00:09:17,684 --> 00:09:19,953
BUBBLE CUTTER!

179
00:09:20,053 --> 00:09:21,955
HIGH‐SPEED ROTATION
TURNS THE BUBBLES

180
00:09:22,055 --> 00:09:23,957
INTO A SALVO OF DEADLY DISKS.

181
00:09:24,024 --> 00:09:26,793
HAMON ENSURES THEY WON'T POP
ALONG THE WAY.

182
00:09:26,860 --> 00:09:27,794
Wamuu: HMM?

183
00:09:27,861 --> 00:09:29,195
Caesar: THE WIND PROTECTING YOU

184
00:09:29,262 --> 00:09:32,132
IS NOTHING MORE THAN A POCKET
OF EMPTY AIR TO THEM.

185
00:09:32,232 --> 00:09:35,969
INSTEAD OF DEFENDING YOU,
IT'LL SUCK THEM IN.

186
00:09:36,036 --> 00:09:38,071
( Wamuu screams )

187
00:09:38,138 --> 00:09:40,907
I UNDERESTIMATED
HIS SKILL WITH HAMON.

188
00:09:40,974 --> 00:09:43,476
IT IS FAR MORE
THAN I BARGAINED FOR.

189
00:09:43,577 --> 00:09:44,477
Caesar: HEH.

190
00:09:45,812 --> 00:09:47,313
Wamuu: NOW, HAMON‐USER...

191
00:09:47,380 --> 00:09:50,651
Caesar: HOLD IT.
I WON'T LET YOU GO INSIDE.

192
00:09:50,751 --> 00:09:53,319
GLIDING BUBBLE CUTTER!

193
00:09:54,655 --> 00:09:56,590
NOW, WHILE YOU'RE
STANDING THERE STUNNED

194
00:09:56,657 --> 00:10:00,100
AND HELPLESSLY OFF BALANCE,
I'LL GIVE YOU A HAMON KICK.

195
00:10:01,434 --> 00:10:04,705
Narrator: BUT CAESAR WAS IN
FOR AN EXTREMELY BIG SHOCK.

196
00:10:04,771 --> 00:10:08,441
IF YOU ARE TRIPPED,
YOU TRY YOUR BEST NOT TO FALL,

197
00:10:08,509 --> 00:10:12,278
ESPECIALLY IF YOU NEED TO AVOID
SUNLIGHT IN ORDER TO SURVIVE.

198
00:10:12,378 --> 00:10:14,447
‐ BUT WAMUU WAS DIFFERENT.
‐ ( Wamuu growls )

199
00:10:14,515 --> 00:10:16,583
Narrator: HE BENT OVER BACKWARDS
AND ATTACKED.

200
00:10:16,617 --> 00:10:18,752
( Caesar groans )

201
00:10:18,785 --> 00:10:20,521
♪

202
00:10:26,359 --> 00:10:29,262
I'VE NEVER SEEN
ANYTHING LIKE THAT BEFORE.

203
00:10:29,295 --> 00:10:32,132
HE'S NOT JUST AN IMMORTAL
WITH INCREDIBLE STRENGTH.

204
00:10:32,232 --> 00:10:35,101
WITH SENSES LIKE THAT,
HE'S A FIGHTING GENIUS.

205
00:10:36,136 --> 00:10:38,138
BUT MY BUBBLE CUTTER

206
00:10:38,204 --> 00:10:41,908
MUST HAVE INFLICTED
SEVERE DAMAGE ON HIM.

207
00:10:41,975 --> 00:10:44,110
THE ADVANTAGE HERE IS MINE!

208
00:10:44,144 --> 00:10:48,281
I HAVE A WAY TO TAKE YOU DOWN,
EVEN INDOORS.

209
00:10:59,325 --> 00:11:02,836
MY NERVES ARE HONED
TO A RAZOR'S EDGE.

210
00:11:02,936 --> 00:11:05,171
I CAN FEEL
DIFFERENCES IN THE AIR.

211
00:11:05,238 --> 00:11:08,174
I HAVE THE ITCH
LIKE WHEN I WAS POOR.

212
00:11:08,241 --> 00:11:10,944
MY BREATHING
IS RELAXED AND NORMAL.

213
00:11:11,011 --> 00:11:12,245
I'M NOT SWEATING.

214
00:11:12,312 --> 00:11:14,848
PERFECT HAMON CONDITIONS.

215
00:11:14,948 --> 00:11:17,017
( gasps )

216
00:11:17,117 --> 00:11:19,019
INSTRUCTOR MESHINA!

217
00:11:19,085 --> 00:11:20,521
( Meshina groans )

218
00:11:20,587 --> 00:11:22,689
‐ ( feet shuffle )
‐ ( Caesar gasps )

219
00:11:25,526 --> 00:11:31,097
I SEE YOU'VE TAKEN OFF YOUR COAT
AND MADE YOURSELF READY, WAMUU.

220
00:11:37,671 --> 00:11:39,540
( wind blowing )

221
00:11:40,874 --> 00:11:44,044
JoJo: DAMN IT.
CAESAR AND MESHINA AREN'T HERE.

222
00:11:44,144 --> 00:11:47,447
DO YOU THINK THEY
MIGHT HAVE ALREADY GONE INSIDE?

223
00:11:49,049 --> 00:11:52,886
Lisa Lisa: NO. THAT'S HIS‐‐
THAT'S MESHINA'S ARM.

224
00:11:52,986 --> 00:11:56,657
Caesar: NOW TAKE THIS!
BUBBLE LAUNCHER!

225
00:11:56,723 --> 00:11:58,992
Wamuu: THAT'S NOTHING.

226
00:11:59,059 --> 00:12:01,401
♪

227
00:12:05,005 --> 00:12:06,472
Caesar: BUBBLE CUTTER!

228
00:12:07,741 --> 00:12:08,742
RUNNING? HAH!

229
00:12:08,809 --> 00:12:11,244
Wamuu: I WON'T RUN
OR HIDE FROM YOU!

230
00:12:17,584 --> 00:12:20,353
( gasps ) HUH?

231
00:12:20,420 --> 00:12:23,223
( Caesar breathes deeply )

232
00:12:25,091 --> 00:12:26,059
( chuckles )

233
00:12:26,092 --> 00:12:27,828
( Wamuu growls )

234
00:12:27,894 --> 00:12:29,530
Caesar: BUBBLE CUTTER!

235
00:12:34,835 --> 00:12:35,769
YOU'RE DEAD, WAMUU!

236
00:12:35,869 --> 00:12:39,205
GLIDING BUBBLE CUTTER!

237
00:12:39,272 --> 00:12:41,775
( Wamuu groans )

238
00:12:46,012 --> 00:12:48,214
Caesar: WAMUU!

239
00:12:48,281 --> 00:12:51,351
Wamuu: I'M FINISHED
WITH THESE GAMES.

240
00:12:51,417 --> 00:12:53,053
YOU'RE THROUGH.

241
00:12:53,119 --> 00:12:55,088
♪

242
00:12:55,121 --> 00:12:56,089
DIVINE SAND‐‐

243
00:12:56,122 --> 00:12:57,390
Caesar: WAIT A MINUTE, WAMUU.

244
00:12:57,457 --> 00:12:58,625
STOP, AND LOOK AROUND.

245
00:12:59,726 --> 00:13:00,701
Wamuu: HUH?

246
00:13:00,767 --> 00:13:02,068
Caesar: MY BUBBLE CUTTERS

247
00:13:02,135 --> 00:13:03,637
ARE NOW BUBBLE LENSES,

248
00:13:03,737 --> 00:13:06,540
AND THEY'RE FLOATING
IN THE AIR ALL AROUND YOU.

249
00:13:06,607 --> 00:13:09,576
AND THAT ENORMOUS HOLE
YOU KNOCKED IN THE WALL EARLIER

250
00:13:09,643 --> 00:13:13,747
IS JUST LIKE THE OPEN SHUTTER OF
A CAMERA ON A BRIGHT SUMMER DAY.

251
00:13:13,814 --> 00:13:17,450
THOSE LENSES,
THEY FOCUS THE SUNLIGHT...

252
00:13:18,819 --> 00:13:20,821
INTO THE HOTEL.

253
00:13:20,921 --> 00:13:22,422
Wamuu: WHAT?!

254
00:13:23,657 --> 00:13:26,226
( screams )

255
00:13:26,292 --> 00:13:27,628
Caesar: YOU CAN'T MOVE.

256
00:13:27,661 --> 00:13:30,230
YOU'RE LIKE FILM,
A FROZEN IMAGE.

257
00:13:30,296 --> 00:13:32,999
YOU'RE TOTALLY EXPOSED, WAMUU.

258
00:13:33,066 --> 00:13:35,268
( Wamuu groaning )

259
00:13:35,335 --> 00:13:37,738
( Caesar gasps )
TRYING YOUR VAPOR BARRIER AGAIN?

260
00:13:37,804 --> 00:13:39,172
NOT THIS TIME.

261
00:13:39,239 --> 00:13:41,341
NOW, WAMUU,
I'M GOING TO FINISH YOU OFF

262
00:13:41,407 --> 00:13:43,176
WITH A DIRECT HAMON BLAST.

263
00:13:43,243 --> 00:13:46,346
Narrator: ONE POINT
AT ONE MOMENT,

264
00:13:46,412 --> 00:13:48,181
A TINY BLIND SPOT.

265
00:13:49,415 --> 00:13:51,618
CAESAR'S BODY CREATED
THE BRIEFEST OF SHADOWS

266
00:13:51,685 --> 00:13:53,486
AMID THE BLAZING WALL
OF SUNLIGHT.

267
00:13:53,520 --> 00:13:56,156
WAMUU DIDN'T WASTE HIS CHANCE.

268
00:13:56,189 --> 00:13:57,323
( Caesar gasps )

269
00:13:57,357 --> 00:13:58,959
Narrator:
HE SHOWED CAESAR ONCE AGAIN

270
00:13:59,025 --> 00:14:02,368
THAT HE WAS A FIGHTING GENIUS
AND A GENIUS OF STRATEGY.

271
00:14:02,435 --> 00:14:05,939
Wamuu: WIND POWER,
DIVINE SANDSTORM!

272
00:14:06,006 --> 00:14:08,809
♪

273
00:14:10,711 --> 00:14:11,645
( both gasp )

274
00:14:15,115 --> 00:14:18,284
JoJo: HUH? S‐SUCH DESTRUCTION.

275
00:14:18,351 --> 00:14:19,820
Lisa Lisa: IT COULDN'T BE.

276
00:14:19,886 --> 00:14:21,387
JoJo: IT'S WAMUU'S
DIVINE SANDSTORM.

277
00:14:21,487 --> 00:14:22,556
I'M SURE OF IT.

278
00:14:22,656 --> 00:14:24,858
Lisa Lisa: SO THAT MEANS
CAESAR IS....

279
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:28,161
( Wamuu chuckles )

280
00:14:28,228 --> 00:14:31,665
YOU HAD GROWN SO MUCH
IN SO LITTLE TIME.

281
00:14:31,732 --> 00:14:33,066
I'M SATISFIED.

282
00:14:33,166 --> 00:14:37,738
I HAVEN'T HAD A FIGHT LIKE THAT
IN AGES NOW, WARRIOR OF HAMON.

283
00:14:37,838 --> 00:14:40,541
( groans )

284
00:14:40,574 --> 00:14:43,409
AND IT WAS A CLOSE ONE AS WELL.

285
00:14:43,510 --> 00:14:46,146
IF THE WIND
OF MY DIVINE SANDSTORM

286
00:14:46,212 --> 00:14:50,383
HADN'T HAD THE STRENGTH TO BLOW
YOUR BUBBLE SENSES TO OBLIVION,

287
00:14:50,416 --> 00:14:53,854
I HAVE NO IDEA HOW
I WOULD HAVE STOPPED THE LIGHT

288
00:14:53,920 --> 00:14:55,822
BEFORE IT DESTROYED ME.

289
00:14:55,889 --> 00:14:59,893
AND EVEN IF THE MIGHTY
LORD KARS, WHO CANNOT USE WIND,

290
00:14:59,926 --> 00:15:02,536
HAD BEEN THE ONE
TO FIRST NOTE YOUR PRESENCE

291
00:15:02,603 --> 00:15:05,672
AND CONFRONT YOU AS I DID
AND FACED YOUR POWER‐‐

292
00:15:05,739 --> 00:15:07,774
( groaning )

293
00:15:09,109 --> 00:15:10,443
IF HE HAD PREVAILED,

294
00:15:10,544 --> 00:15:13,714
HE MOST CERTAINLY WOULD HAVE
BEEN IN FAR WORSE SHAPE

295
00:15:13,780 --> 00:15:16,382
THAN I FIND MYSELF IN NOW. HUH?

296
00:15:17,518 --> 00:15:20,386
( Caesar panting )

297
00:15:23,757 --> 00:15:25,959
Wamuu: ENOUGH.
YOU WILL NOT FIGHT AGAIN,

298
00:15:26,026 --> 00:15:28,695
FOR YOU HAVE NOTHING LEFT
WITH WHICH TO FIGHT.

299
00:15:28,762 --> 00:15:32,198
MY DIVINE SANDSTORM
HAS SHREDDED YOUR BODY

300
00:15:32,265 --> 00:15:34,735
BEYOND ANY CHANCE OF SURVIVAL.

301
00:15:34,801 --> 00:15:36,202
‐ ( Caesar yells )
‐ Wamuu: STOP.

302
00:15:36,269 --> 00:15:38,639
‐ THE BATTLE IS OVER.
‐ ( Caesar panting )

303
00:15:38,739 --> 00:15:42,743
Wamuu: YOU HAVE NO MORE HAMON
WITH WHICH TO CONTINUE. SEE?

304
00:15:42,809 --> 00:15:46,479
YOU'VE ALMOST
COMPLETELY BLED OUT.

305
00:15:46,580 --> 00:15:50,316
THAT MEANS YOU HAVE NO HOPE.

306
00:15:55,321 --> 00:15:56,489
STOP, CAESAR.

307
00:16:00,894 --> 00:16:05,639
GOODBYE. YOUR LIFE AND
ALL YOU ONCE WERE HAS ENDED.

308
00:16:09,510 --> 00:16:10,677
( gasps ) WHAT?

309
00:16:12,178 --> 00:16:13,113
( Caesar chuckles )

310
00:16:18,451 --> 00:16:20,420
Wamuu: MY LIP RING
WITH THE ANTIDOTE,

311
00:16:20,486 --> 00:16:21,788
WHY DID YOU TAKE IT?

312
00:16:21,855 --> 00:16:26,527
Caesar: I‐I'M NOT AFRAID
TO DIE HERE...

313
00:16:27,794 --> 00:16:32,098
BUT I AM A PROUD MEMBER
OF THE ZEPPELI FAMILY,

314
00:16:32,165 --> 00:16:34,167
SO YOU SEE, IT'S IN MY BLOOD.

315
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:38,605
SOMETHING LIKE THIS
MIGHT MEAN ABSOLUTELY NOTHING

316
00:16:38,672 --> 00:16:41,975
TO A DEMENTED,
INHUMAN MONSTER LIKE YOU.

317
00:16:42,876 --> 00:16:45,879
MY FATHER DIDN'T RECOGNIZE ME,

318
00:16:45,946 --> 00:16:49,816
BUT HE SACRIFICED HIS LIFE
TO SAVE MINE ANYWAY.

319
00:16:49,883 --> 00:16:52,786
MY GRANDFATHER
GAVE HIS HAMON ENERGY

320
00:16:52,853 --> 00:16:57,057
TO SAVE JOJO'S GRANDFATHER
RIGHT BEFORE HE DIED.

321
00:16:59,225 --> 00:17:00,226
IT'S TRADITION.

322
00:17:00,293 --> 00:17:01,234
( gags )

323
00:17:01,301 --> 00:17:03,403
I HAVE TO DO SOMETHING.

324
00:17:03,469 --> 00:17:09,543
I‐I CAN'T LET MY LIFE'S FLAME
JUST SPUTTER OUT TO DARKNESS.

325
00:17:09,576 --> 00:17:12,746
THIS IS
THE ZEPPELI FAMILY SPIRIT,

326
00:17:12,846 --> 00:17:16,349
HANDED DOWN FROM THE PAST
TO ENSURE THE FAMILY'S FUTURE.

327
00:17:16,416 --> 00:17:19,085
IT'S THE HUMAN SPIRIT!

328
00:17:24,024 --> 00:17:28,829
JOJO, THIS IS
THE LAST OF MY HAMON!

329
00:17:28,895 --> 00:17:33,033
TAKE IT FROM ME!

330
00:17:33,099 --> 00:17:36,570
TAKE IT FROM ME!

331
00:17:36,603 --> 00:17:39,039
( both gasp )

332
00:17:39,105 --> 00:17:40,607
JoJo: DID YOU HEAR THAT?

333
00:17:40,674 --> 00:17:42,776
IT SOUNDED
LIKE CAESAR SCREAMING.

334
00:17:42,876 --> 00:17:45,779
Lisa Lisa: YES, I HEARD IT.
OH, NO. CAESAR CAN'T....

335
00:17:48,281 --> 00:17:52,385
JoJo: CAESAR!

336
00:17:52,452 --> 00:17:54,555
♪

337
00:18:03,804 --> 00:18:07,273
Wamuu: HE MADE
A BUBBLE FROM HIS BLOOD.

338
00:18:07,307 --> 00:18:11,712
HE MUST HAVE USED EVERY LAST BIT
OF HIS HAMON TO MAKE IT.

339
00:18:11,778 --> 00:18:14,815
BEFORE HE DIED,
HE SAVED IT FOR HIS FRIENDS

340
00:18:14,915 --> 00:18:17,951
RATHER THAN USING IT
TO TRY AND DESTROY ME.

341
00:18:24,324 --> 00:18:26,660
I'LL LET IT GO,

342
00:18:26,760 --> 00:18:29,996
BUT NOT BECAUSE
I'M SENTIMENTAL ABOUT HIM.

343
00:18:30,096 --> 00:18:33,834
HIS TALENT AS A FIGHTER
WAS UNDENIABLE.

344
00:18:33,900 --> 00:18:36,970
HE HAS MY DEEP RESPECT
AS A FELLOW WARRIOR.

345
00:18:37,003 --> 00:18:40,674
I WILL HOLD YOU AND THE LAST
MOMENTS WE SPENT TOGETHER

346
00:18:40,774 --> 00:18:42,809
FOREVER IN MY MEMORY, CAESAR...

347
00:18:44,010 --> 00:18:47,514
A MAN AS SPLENDID
AND AS FLEETING

348
00:18:47,581 --> 00:18:49,850
AS THE BUBBLES HE CONJURED.

349
00:18:49,916 --> 00:18:51,852
♪

350
00:18:55,121 --> 00:18:57,123
( stones clatter )

351
00:19:00,426 --> 00:19:03,369
JoJo: THE PLACE IS A WRECK.

352
00:19:03,436 --> 00:19:05,772
A DIVINE SANDSTORM DID ALL THIS,

353
00:19:05,839 --> 00:19:09,375
AND CAESAR WAS CAUGHT
RIGHT INSIDE THE HEART OF IT.

354
00:19:09,475 --> 00:19:11,144
( both gasp )

355
00:19:13,614 --> 00:19:15,148
A BUBBLE.

356
00:19:16,216 --> 00:19:17,684
C‐COULD IT BE?

357
00:19:17,718 --> 00:19:19,152
LOOK AT THAT.

358
00:19:20,621 --> 00:19:23,557
INSIDE IS CAESAR'S BANDANA.

359
00:19:23,624 --> 00:19:25,726
ALSO A RING,

360
00:19:25,826 --> 00:19:27,728
WAMUU'S LIP RING.

361
00:19:30,196 --> 00:19:31,131
( yelps )

362
00:19:31,197 --> 00:19:34,334
THIS HAMON ENERGY
FEELS REALLY STRANGE.

363
00:19:34,400 --> 00:19:37,003
W‐WHOA!

364
00:19:39,072 --> 00:19:41,341
( gasping )

365
00:19:45,679 --> 00:19:48,048
YOU KNOW, I HAVEN'T
BEEN ABLE TO BRING MYSELF

366
00:19:48,081 --> 00:19:51,752
TO CALL CAESAR'S NAME SINCE WE
MADE OUR WAY INTO THIS PLACE.

367
00:19:51,852 --> 00:19:55,689
IT'S BECAUSE I'M AFRAID
THERE'LL BE NO ANSWER.

368
00:19:55,756 --> 00:19:58,925
IF I CAME IN HERE
AND CRIED OUT HIS NAME,

369
00:19:59,025 --> 00:20:01,668
THERE MIGHT NOT BE
ANY RESPONSE IN RETURN.

370
00:20:01,702 --> 00:20:04,370
THERE MIGHT BE NOTHING
BUT A LIFELESS SILENCE.

371
00:20:04,470 --> 00:20:05,872
THAT IS WHAT SCARES ME.

372
00:20:05,939 --> 00:20:09,142
I COULDN'T ACCEPT IT,
SO I DIDN'T CALL HIS NAME.

373
00:20:09,209 --> 00:20:13,313
‐ BUT NOW I KNOW HE'S GONE.
‐ ( man singing opera )

374
00:20:13,379 --> 00:20:15,115
THE HAMON
CONTAINED IN THAT BUBBLE

375
00:20:15,181 --> 00:20:17,884
TOLD ME EVERYTHING
I NEEDED TO KNOW.

376
00:20:19,219 --> 00:20:20,521
RIGHT HERE,

377
00:20:20,554 --> 00:20:24,725
JUST A FEW MOMENTS AGO,
CAESAR DIED.

378
00:20:24,825 --> 00:20:26,727
GUH! CAESAR, YOU BASTARD.

379
00:20:26,793 --> 00:20:30,664
YOU HAD TO BE A DAMN SHOWOFF
RIGHT UP UNTIL THE VERY END,

380
00:20:30,731 --> 00:20:31,898
AND THEN YOU LEAVE

381
00:20:31,965 --> 00:20:34,300
A PRECIOUS GIFT
LIKE THIS FOR ME.

382
00:20:34,367 --> 00:20:36,670
CAESAR, WHERE ARE YOU?!

383
00:20:36,737 --> 00:20:39,372
WHERE THE HELL
ARE YOU SLEEPING?

384
00:20:39,405 --> 00:20:41,074
I'LL FIND YOU, CAESAR.

385
00:20:41,141 --> 00:20:42,643
I'LL DIG YOU UP.

386
00:20:42,709 --> 00:20:44,210
‐ CAESAR!
‐ Lisa Lisa: JOJO.

387
00:20:44,244 --> 00:20:47,413
THIS ISN'T THE TIME
TO SEARCH OR GRIEVE.

388
00:20:47,480 --> 00:20:49,149
‐ WE HAVE WORK TO DO.
‐ JoJo: WHAT?

389
00:20:49,215 --> 00:20:52,218
Lisa Lisa: THERE ARE
TWO OF THEM AND TWO OF US.

390
00:20:52,252 --> 00:20:54,755
THE NUMBERS ARE BALANCED.
THEY'RE EVEN.

391
00:20:54,855 --> 00:20:57,824
THAT TRAIL OF BLOOD
LEADING UP THE STAIRS

392
00:20:57,891 --> 00:21:01,535
TELLS ME THAT CAESAR
SIGNIFICANTLY WOUNDED WAMUU.

393
00:21:01,602 --> 00:21:04,370
WE'RE IN THE MIDDLE
OF ENEMY TERRITORY.

394
00:21:04,437 --> 00:21:07,007
LET'S GO FINISH THIS FIGHT.

395
00:21:07,073 --> 00:21:08,875
JOJO, COME ON.

396
00:21:08,942 --> 00:21:12,913
TAKE THE ANTIDOTE. THEN WE'LL
GO HUNT THOSE BASTARDS DOWN.

397
00:21:12,946 --> 00:21:14,447
( JoJo scoffs )
THAT HEARTLESS‐‐

398
00:21:14,515 --> 00:21:18,384
SHE CAN'T EVEN MANAGE TO SHED
A SINGLE TEAR FOR CAESAR.

399
00:21:18,451 --> 00:21:19,586
( sputters )

400
00:21:19,620 --> 00:21:21,755
♪

401
00:21:27,594 --> 00:21:29,095
COACH LISA LISA,

402
00:21:29,129 --> 00:21:32,733
YOUR CIGARETTE, IT'S BACKWARDS.

403
00:21:36,770 --> 00:21:38,138
LISA LISA IS OUR COACH,

404
00:21:38,238 --> 00:21:40,974
SO SHE ALWAYS HAS TO KEEP
A COOL EXTERIOR.

405
00:21:41,074 --> 00:21:45,546
I KNOW SHE WANTS TO CRY
MUCH MORE THAN I DO.

406
00:21:45,612 --> 00:21:47,313
HE TREATED HER LIKE A GODDESS

407
00:21:47,413 --> 00:21:50,216
AND KNEW HER LONGER
THAN I'VE KNOWN HER.

408
00:21:52,118 --> 00:21:55,989
I HAVE TO TRY
AND HOLD MY FEELINGS BACK.

409
00:21:58,124 --> 00:22:00,661
CAESAR,
I KNOW YOU ALWAYS THOUGHT

410
00:22:00,761 --> 00:22:02,836
I WAS IMPULSIVE
AND SELF‐CENTERED,

411
00:22:02,903 --> 00:22:05,005
BUT SOMETIMES I DO UNDERSTAND

412
00:22:05,105 --> 00:22:07,340
THE FEELINGS
OF THOSE AROUND ME.

413
00:22:07,407 --> 00:22:10,010
I MIGHT FINALLY BE LEARNING.

414
00:22:10,110 --> 00:22:12,946
I SWEAR I WILL FIGHT THEM
BOTH LIKE THE DEVIL

415
00:22:13,013 --> 00:22:14,748
UNTIL THERE'S
NOTHING LEFT OF THEM.

416
00:22:14,815 --> 00:22:16,517
I'LL AVENGE YOU, CAESAR.

417
00:22:16,583 --> 00:22:18,184
YOUR SPIRIT IS WITH ME.

418
00:22:20,253 --> 00:22:22,823
♪

419
00:22:25,491 --> 00:22:28,428
BLOOD. HIS BLOOD.

420
00:22:28,494 --> 00:22:31,364
THIS IS WHERE HE FELL.

421
00:22:32,533 --> 00:22:34,334
CAESAR.

422
00:22:34,367 --> 00:22:36,336
( Lisa Lisa crying )

423
00:22:40,507 --> 00:22:42,442
CAESAR.

424
00:22:45,879 --> 00:22:49,382
JoJo: CAESAR!

425
00:22:49,482 --> 00:22:51,217
♪

426
00:22:51,317 --> 00:22:53,720
Narrator: THEY WERE DEEP
IN ENEMY TERRITORY.

427
00:22:53,787 --> 00:22:56,222
KARS AND WAMUU WERE VERY NEARBY,

428
00:22:56,289 --> 00:22:59,660
BUT THE TWO SIMPLY
COULDN'T HELP THEMSELVES.

429
00:22:59,726 --> 00:23:02,836
JOJO CALLED OUT CAESAR'S NAME.

430
00:23:02,903 --> 00:23:06,239
LISA LISA'S TEARS FLOWED FREELY.

431
00:23:06,339 --> 00:23:09,676
BUT THEIR
HEARTBROKEN CRIES OF GRIEF

432
00:23:09,743 --> 00:23:12,478
WERE ANSWERED ONLY
BY A COLD SILENCE.

433
00:23:12,546 --> 00:23:16,750
CAESAR WAS GONE.

434
00:23:16,850 --> 00:23:18,318
AS THEY MOURNED HIM,

435
00:23:18,384 --> 00:23:22,523
THEY TOOK SOLACE
IN ONE SIMPLE FACT.

436
00:23:22,589 --> 00:23:24,991
THOUGH HIS BODY HAD DIED,

437
00:23:25,058 --> 00:23:27,928
HIS SOUL WOULD LIVE ON
THROUGH THEM.

438
00:23:28,028 --> 00:23:31,431
REST IN PEACE, CAESAR ZEPPELI.

439
00:23:37,604 --> 00:23:39,540
♪

440
00:23:52,619 --> 00:23:56,222
♪ IN AND AROUND THE LAKE

441
00:23:56,289 --> 00:23:58,892
♪ MOUNTAINS COME
OUT OF THE SKY ♪

442
00:23:58,959 --> 00:24:03,069
♪ THEY STAND THERE

443
00:24:03,136 --> 00:24:04,871
♪ 24 BEFORE, MY LOVE

444
00:24:04,938 --> 00:24:10,310
♪ AND I'LL BE THERE

445
00:25:08,208 --> 00:25:09,976
♪

446
00:25:10,043 --> 00:25:12,012
Lisa Lisa: YOU'RE REALLY
NOT IMPRESSING ME.

447
00:25:12,045 --> 00:25:14,180
Vampire: I'M GOING
TO HUG YOU TO DEATH!

448
00:25:14,214 --> 00:25:16,883
Wamuu: WE FIGHT TONIGHT
UNDER THE FULL MOON.

449
00:25:16,983 --> 00:25:18,451
Kars: YOU HAVE NO TOMORROW.

450
00:25:18,519 --> 00:25:21,154
JoJo: WE'LL FACE
THIS FIGHT TOGETHER, CAESAR.

